    <h2>Here are some additional post-adoption tips and information to help you and your pet thrive together:</h2>
    <ol type="1">
        <li>Socialize your pet: Socializing your pet with other animals and people is important for their development and can help prevent behavioral issues. Start by introducing your pet to new people and animals gradually, and always supervise their interactions.        </li>
        <li>Provide a safe and comfortable living space: Make sure your pet has a comfortable and safe place to sleep and relax. Provide them with a cozy bed and plenty of toys and enrichment activities to keep them mentally stimulated.</li> 
        <li>Consider pet insurance: Pet insurance can help cover unexpected vet bills and provide peace of mind in case of an emergency. Research different plans and providers to find the best option for you and your pet.</li>
    </ol>
